trait-background-magical-encounter-name = Intrinsic Augments
trait-background-magical-encounter-description = Through cyberware, bioware, genetic modifications, psionics or birthright, you gain access to a set of abilities some would call unnatural.

trait-background-chromehead-name = Chromehead
trait-background-chromehead-description = For most, cybernetics are something they install out of necessity, or a temporary upgrade. But for you body modifications is the way of living. A significant portion of your income and free time goes into seeking and aquiring more cyberware. Get +3 points to spend on cyberware in character creation. 